        <updateDate>2007-04-26T17:56:37Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Prohibits the Secretary from making a loan or loans to any entity in excess of $1 billion in the aggregate over a five-year period unless the loan exceeding the limit is approved by joint resolution no later than six months after notice is provided to Congress.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
